These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, teacher
1. the mechanic is in an even position##4
2. the teacher is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Game   | mah-jongg | scrabble |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk
2 different games are played: whist, domino
1. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee        |
| Game      | whist  | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, azure
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Color   | azure    | chestnut |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, cricket
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, mango
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Sport   | basketball      | cricket |
| Food       | broccoli | mango    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dannemann
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, polish
1. the dutch is in an even position##4
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Cigar           | tiparillo | dannemann |
| Nationality   | polish    | dutch         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
