.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, aquamarine
1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime      |
| Color         | white | aquamarine |

