.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, december
2 different pets are kept: goat, turtle
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |   2    |
| Birthday   | june | december  |
| Pet   | goat      | turtle |

 